            <bug_when>2013-08-12 17:47:47 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Some documentations for events are not shown with the 3.0 API Viewer. The event is marked as documented only the text is missing.

Open the current API Viewer:
http://demo.qooxdoo.org/3.0/apiviewer/#qx.ui.core.Widget~beforeContextmenuOpen

As you can see the text for the event &quot;beforeContextmenuOpen&quot; is not displayed.

With the 2.1.1 the API Viewer:
http://demo.qooxdoo.org/2.1.1/apiviewer/#qx.ui.core.Widget~beforeContextmenuOpen

It works like expected.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
